{"tid":30984,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"王俊杰（杰仔）咁既水平就學做軍師真係笑撚死人","createTime":"2016-12-09T11:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T13:42:08.000Z","uid":34884,"like":18,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9355023b0310534f22d8ce8e81131222ef1fda8","tid":30984,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/09/193302_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F09%2F193302_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f7e51c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出得呢啲單打Post，證明王俊杰呢班軍師係得咁上下料子<br />\n<br />\n首先梁振英得罪晒泛民建制既人<br />\n如果佢唔連任，佢落台之後就會受到好嚴重既清算<br />\n就算佢唔想做都要焗做<br />\n<br />\n第二如果佢一開始就打算唔連任，佢冇必要同袁國強入稟DQ議員，搞咁大件事，hea做多半年仲好<br />\n<br />\n第三如果佢冇諗住連任，上幾次記者問佢會唔會爭取連任就唔會顧左右而言他，亦唔需要連選委都未定就特登開記者會出嚟話唔選<br />\n<br />\n今日梁振英用「專心照顧家人」呢種同腳痛一樣咁牽強既理由講唔選，幾乎可以肯定佢同中共傾掂數，落台後唔會清算佢（又或者冇咁大力），分分鐘可以返大陸做大官<br />\n<br />\n所以之前話梁振英DQ梁游係為左連任推論唔係錯，亦同梁振英依家出嚟話唔選係冇關係<br />\n<br />\n再講智者邊夠你嚟呀王俊杰<br />\n一早知梁振英唔會連任你又唔早講<br />\n你都係返去港大圍爐打飛機啦傻仔<br />\n<br />\n順帶一提其實梁振英星期五先出嚟話唔選係因為中共想為後日既選委做人事佈局<br />\nKO一個梁振英就足以令嗰班候選選委方寸大亂<br />\n<br />\n睇得穿呢樣野既唔該畀負評<br />\n畀我知道有幾多人有正常水平"},{"pid":"f45e6b1728b2f90f0d7dc9949f378355fdd6180e","tid":30984,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"再講依家就話唔爭取連任唔代表選完選委之後唔會反口"},{"pid":"4dd1192a09820110aa31c38a8e677b01d495b25e","tid":30984,"uid":11830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"御理咁既水平走去笑人真係笑死人<br />\n<br />\n返高登圍爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"243d45aa2578b9a5d6b14497edfce6575844e465","tid":30984,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>御理咁既水平走去笑人真係笑死人<br />\n<br />\n返高登圍爐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你愈叫我走我係唔撚走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36345a57333b267f2a8b1098966b4f4bb06ffc5f","tid":30984,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"😸危殆bb一鍵留名！！"},{"pid":"bbd01b1ff466b93f3590360a34c06c06e3c798aa","tid":30984,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"又批鬥"},{"pid":"e3b6f6157a7542c2ff36f74055856c5bcce6d318","tid":30984,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"睇得穿呢樣野既唔該畀負評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a091831e149e341b8d39ba93e9c11a59110e8c15","tid":30984,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇得穿呢樣野既唔該畀負評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明益你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad13672ee97defe755a4071865d3207bb5cb733","tid":30984,"uid":34867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"依家唔抽唔通留返拜山先抽咩"},{"pid":"f97114b4943fb742768231bb136808ed3bbd2631","tid":30984,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"一句講曬,依家佢兩個有冇幫到689連任?"},{"pid":"bcf1c608e6a8c6045ca8167c461dd37f9fb7496c","tid":30984,"uid":38665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T12:57:12.000Z","msg":"屌，做咩班熱狗打手又過晒嚟污染呢邊<br />\n王俊杰講乜關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"2c6da30b4d8d32788d36a36b3fb7fc7811f5